</span>
<span>Surfers Paradise, Queensland, Australia</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>Lan Spa provides personalized spa treatments, including luxury facials and body massages designed for optimal relaxation and rejuvenation. The company's ethos of luxury and tranquility is reflected in its website's refined color scheme, complementing the introductory hero video that showcases the spa's welcoming atmosphere and high-quality services.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-plus.svg" alt="plus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>The home page is content-rich with a client testimonials section that lends credibility to the site, while the introductory video depicting a day at the spa with a selection of relaxing treatments effectively advertises its brand.</p></div></div><div
class="entry-website-cons">
<span
class="icon icon-sm">
<img
src="/assets/images/icon-minus.svg" alt="minus sign" width="18" height="18" />
</span><div
class="entry-text"><p>WAVE picked up several instances of insufficient contrast ratios throughout the website. The lack of promotional offers or monthly specials may deter visitors on a budget from trying the spa's services.</p></div></div></div><h4>Desktop Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-desktop"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-lan-spa-3840x10551-20240613.webp"
data-type="desktop"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-lan-spa-3840x10551-20240613.webp?crop=400:248,offset-x0,offset-y0&width=400&dpr=2"
alt="desktop screenshot of website"
width="400"
height="248"
/></div>
<img
class="lightbox-thumbnail-magnifier"
src="/assets/images/icon-magnifying.svg"
alt="magnifying glass"
width="50"
height="50"
/></div><div
class="entry-text"><p>On larger screens, there is ample breathing room for the video content and images to really pop. The desktop site also has a good mix of white space and text to not seem overwhelming and still provide visual appeal. The desktop site boasts a high performance score of 97/100 on Google's PageSpeed Insights test.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
class="entry-website-mobile"><div
data-src="https://www.zarla.com/images/zarla-lan-spa-824x10862-20240613.webp"
data-type="mobile"
class="lightbox-trigger js-lightbox-trigger"
><div
class="lightbox-thumbnail">
<img
class="lazyload"
