class="entry-text"><p>The mobile site keeps the images and video high-quality, while the content slims down nicely without losing readability. The online booking process is seamless, and users can easily access vital information, although the website would benefit from additional CTA buttons to accentuate certain page sections. On Google's PageSpeed Insights test, the site has a higher-than-average performance score of 96/100.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
